\begin_inset Formula $R\rightarrow\infty$
\end_inset

 which happens as 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta\rightarrow\arccos(-1/e)$
\end_inset

.
 Due to even symetry of the cosine function, 
\begin_inset Formula $R\rightarrow-\infty$
\end_inset

 which happens as 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta\rightarrow-\arccos(-1/e)$
\end_inset

.
